Arthur Wontner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Wontner 0 Arthur Wontner (21 January 1875 – 10 July 1960) was a British actor best known for playing Sir Arthur Conan Doyle's master detective Sherlock Holmes in five films from 1931 to 1937.
